des:
With the inspirational quotes skill you can listen to some of the most encouraging words ever written (or spoken!) Hear the words of;

Rosa Parks
Mahatma Ghandi
Albert Einstein
Theodore Roosevelt
Florence Nightingale
Amelia Earhart
Robert Louis Stevenson
Steve Jobs
Eleanor Roosevelt
Anne Frank

And loads more...
